Promiass Ruins
Monster Rancher Metropolis: Monster Rancher Advance 2 Archive (GameBoy Advance): FAQ: Expedition Maps: Promiass Ruins
By Seize on Tuesday, September 30, 2003 - 12:18 am:

To open up this region, beat the Class S Official and you will be at Master Rank. Then begins the invitations to the Big4 and Emperor's Cup (see calendar for dates). Your monster must beat all 4 himself to go to the Emperor's Cup, once you win the Emporer's Cup Promiass opens up.
-GoldenBoy
